                            characteristics that has an association with distance learning and e-learning Park &
                            Wentling (2007).</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="d-flex flex-row">
                    <div class="d-flex flex-row">
                        <div class="p-3 align-self-start">
                            <i class="fa fa-check"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="p-3 align-self-end">
                            <p>The ability of the student to manage their time and to adapt to self-directed nature of
                                online
                                learning Pillay, Irving and Tones (2007).</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="d-flex flex-row">
                    <div class="d-flex flex-row">
                        <div class="p-3 align-self-start">
                            <i class="fa fa-check"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="p-3 align-self-end">
                            <p>A person who has the requisite knowledge, attitudes, skills and habits in technology
                                will have an
                                advantage over the novices (Piskurich, 2003).</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

